485
00:46:34,200 --> 00:46:38,200
¿Tony?

486
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:45,000
¿Qué pasa, Tony?

487
00:46:48,800 --> 00:46:52,800
¿Tony?

488
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:57,000
